snippet.title: Diana and Roma play in the Baby Playroom & NEW Baby Doll
snippet.description:
Parents, learn more about Love, Diana here:
Love Diana Baby Doll Princess and Ballerina: https://bit.ly/3vpFMTU
Diana and Roma want to play in the new playroom. But the playroom is only for babies! Roma goes to the playroom with baby Oliver, and Diana - with new Love Diana baby dolls!
Thanks for watching!
Subscribe to Kids Diana Show - http://bit.ly/2k7NrSx
DIANA Instagram https://www.instagram.com/kidsdianashow/
ROMA Instagram https://www.instagram.com/kidsromashow/

#DianaandRoma #LoveDiana #BabyDoll Facebook https://www.facebook.com/KidsDianaShowOfficial/
